Odaily Planet Daily News GMGN market data shows that Virtual Protocol ecosystem tokens fell across the board today, including: 
VIRTUAL's market value is now $1.01 billion, down 8.6% in 24 hours; 
GAME by Virtuals (GAME)'s market value is now $32 million, down 16.6% in 24 hours; 
VaderAI by Virtuals (VADER)'s market value is now $17 million, down 4.1% in 24 hours; 
Luna by Virtuals (LUNA)'s market value is now $15 million, down 11.3% in 24 hours.

Odaily Planet Daily News According to official news, the Satoshi Ramp mainnet supports cross-chain BTC to the NEAR network. Its features are: 
-2 Bitcoin block confirmations per transaction; 
-2 to 3 US dollars in transaction fees; 
-Use Bitcoin as Gas fee; 
-No NEAR wallet required, that is, 1 Bitcoin wallet
Every DApp on NEAR that integrates the Satoshi protocol allows users to use a Bitcoin wallet to trade their BTC.
